'''FREAK缺陷'''（全称：'''Factoring RSA Export Keys'''，{{lang-zh|'''分解RSA出口级密钥'''}}）是[[传输层安全|SSL/TLS]]协议中的密码学安全缺陷。20世纪90年代，此缺陷随着美国加密出口法规的出台而引入。

==概要==
1990年代时，美国对于货物的出口设立了一些规定，从而引入了这个缺陷。规定中指出，美国软件制造商出口的软件只能使用512位及以下的[[RSA加密演算法|RSA]]加密（即所谓的出口级加密）。此举是为了便于[[NSA|NSA]]破译加密。时至2015年，随着计算能力的发展，破解这种加密已经不再是政府机构才能做到的事，任何人只要拥有充足的计算资源，就能通过[[普通数域筛选法|普通数域筛选法]]加上约100美元的[[云计算|云计算]]服务轻而易举地将其破译。这个缺陷还能和[[中间人攻击|中间人攻击]]结合利用，只要先破译网站的512位弱加密，再发动中间人攻击，就能使任何允许使用512位出口级密钥的网站失去安全保障。此漏洞于2015年发现，但从1990年代开始就已经存在。

FREAK漏洞由IMDEA、[[法国国家信息与自动化研究所|INRIA]]和[[微软研究院|微软研究院]]的研究人员共同发现。<ref name=zdnet20150303>{{cite web|url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/freak-another-day-another-serious-ssl-security-hole/|title=FREAK: Another day, another serious SSL security hole|author=Steven J. Vaughan-Nichols|publisher=ZDNet|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306012011/http://www.zdnet.com/article/freak-another-day-another-serious-ssl-security-hole/|dead-url=no}}</ref> OpenSSL中存在的此漏洞在[[通用漏洞披露|公共漏洞和暴露系统]]中的编号是CVE-2015-0204。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.nvd.nist.gov/view/vuln/detail?vulnId=CVE-2015-0204|title=Vulnerability Summary for CVE-2015-0204|publisher=NIST|date=20 February 2015|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305164508/http://web.nvd.nist.gov/view/vuln/detail?vulnId=CVE-2015-0204|dead-url=no}}</ref>

受到漏洞影响的软件及设备包括[[苹果公司|苹果]]的[[Safari|Safari]]、[[Google|Google]][[安卓|安卓]]系统上的默认浏览器，及[[OpenSSL|OpenSSL]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2015/03/03/freak-flaw-hits-android-and-iphone-users/|title=What The FREAK? Why Android And iPhone Users Need To Pay Attention To The Latest Hot Vulnerability|author=Thomas Fox-Brewster|publisher=Forbes|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306030815/http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2015/03/03/freak-flaw-hits-android-and-iphone-users/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=zdnet20150303/> [[微软|微软]]还表示全版本的[[Windows|Windows]]系统上的SChannel传输层加密实现都受到FREAK漏洞影响。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/03/06/all_microsoft_windows_versions_vulnerable_to_freak/|title=All Microsoft Windows versions are vulnerable to FREAK|publisher=The Register|date=6 March 2015|author=Darren Pauli|accessdate=2015-03-07|archive-date=2015-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307021626/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/03/06/all_microsoft_windows_versions_vulnerable_to_freak/|dead-url=no}}</ref>SChannel中存在的漏洞的CVE编号是CVE-2015-1637。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/security/3046015|title=Microsoft Security Advisory 3046015: Vulnerability in Schannel Could Allow Security Feature Bypass|publisher=Microsoft|date=March 5, 2015|accessdate=2015-03-07|archive-date=2015-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309223746/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/security/3046015|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而苹果的安全传输功能中的漏洞的CVE编号是CVE-2015-1067。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204423 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-03-14 |archive-date=2015-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309201042/https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204423 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

受到漏洞影响的网站包括美国联邦政府网站fbi.gov、whitehouse.gov、nsa.gov，<ref name=timberg2015-03-03/> 一个安全团队的测试发现，36%的被测HTTPS网站都受到漏洞影响。<ref name=fisher2015-03-03/> 根据IP2Location LITE的地理定位，35%的受影响服务器都位于美国。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://infogr.am/https_sites_that_support_rsa_export_suites|title=FREAK Servers By Country|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402104114/http://infogr.am/https_sites_that_support_rsa_export_suites|dead-url=no}}</ref>

有新闻报导称此漏洞是「潜在的灾难」，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/security/2015/03/freak-flaw-in-android-and-apple-devices-cripples-https-crypto-protection/|title="FREAK" flaw in Android and Apple devices cripples HTTPS crypto protection|author=Dan Goodin|publisher=Ars Technica|date=3 March 2015|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150304205803/http://arstechnica.com/security/2015/03/freak-flaw-in-android-and-apple-devices-cripples-https-crypto-protection/|dead-url=no}}</ref>是美国政府意图控制加密技术传播的「{{link-en|意外后果|Unintended consequence}}」。<ref name=timberg2015-03-03>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/the-switch/wp/2015/03/03/freak-flaw-undermines-security-for-apple-and-google-users-researchers-discover/|title=‘FREAK’ flaw undermines security for Apple and Google users, researchers discover|author=Craig Timberg|publisher=Washington Post|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150304014828/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/the-switch/wp/2015/03/03/freak-flaw-undermines-security-for-apple-and-google-users-researchers-discover/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{As of|2015|03|03}}，各软件厂商已在准备发布修复漏洞后的新版本软件。<ref name=timberg2015-03-03/><ref name=fisher2015-03-03>{{cite web|url=https://threatpost.com/new-freak-attack-threatens-many-ssl-clients/111390|title=New FREAK Attack Threatens Many SSL Clients|author=Dennis Fisher|publisher=Threatpost|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306210555/http://threatpost.com/new-freak-attack-threatens-many-ssl-clients/111390|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2015年3月9日，苹果发布了[[iOS_8|iOS 8]]及[[OS_X|OS X]]操作系统的漏洞补丁。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/HT204413|title=About Security Update 2015-002|publisher=Apple|date=March 9, 2015|accessdate=2015-03-14|archive-date=2019-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016162537/https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204413|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.apple.com/HT204423|title=About the security content of iOS 8.2|publisher=Apple|date=March 9, 2015|accessdate=2015-03-14|archive-date=2019-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016162538/https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204423|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2015年3月10日，微软为所有仍在技术支持周期内的Windows系统（[[Windows_Server_2003|Windows Server 2003]]、[[Vista|Vista]]及后续版本）发布了漏洞补丁。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/security/ms15-031.aspx|title=Microsoft Security Bulletin MS15-031 - Important|publisher=Microsoft|date=March 10, 2015|accessdate=2015-03-14|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315142732/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/security/ms15-031.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[Google_Chrome|Google Chrome]] 41和[[Opera|Opera]] 28也已采取相应漏洞缓解措施。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.smacktls.com/#freak |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-03-05 |archive-date=2015-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311112517/https://www.smacktls.com/#freak |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[Mozilla_Firefox|Mozilla Firefox]]不受此漏洞影响。

